0150912050245/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ixEhAAAAIBAJ&sjid=KHQFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2310,2055711&dq=red+skelton+queen&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5pQsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=sfsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3343,6605710&hl=en | title = Skelton replays old comedy skits for royal crowd | author = Thomas, Bob | date = 1984-04-15 | publisher = Lakeland ledger | page = 46 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150912054528/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5pQsAAAAIBAJ&sjid=sfsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=3343,6605710&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2005年，[[公共广播电视公司|公共电视网]]播出特别节目《黄金时代的开拓者》（{{lang|en|''The Pioneers of Primetime''}}），其中有史蒂芬·{{lang|en|F}}·赞伯（{{lang|en|Steven F. Zambo}}）采访斯克尔顿的部分内容，这也是他生前接受的最后几场采访之一<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | date = 2005-07-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325041013/http://www.deseretnews.com/article/600148736/PBS-will-showcase-Pioneers-of-Primetime.html | url = http://www.deseretnews.com/article/600148736/PBS-will-showcase-Pioneers-of-Primetime.html | title = PBS will showcase 'Pioneers of Primetime' | author = Pierce, Scott D. | publisher = The Deseret News | archivedate = 2014-03-25 }}</ref>。

1997年9月17日，经过“漫长且原因不明疾病”折磨的理查德·伯纳德·“雷德”·斯克尔顿在加利福尼亚州[[兰乔米拉_(加利福尼亚州)|兰乔米拉]][[艾森豪威尔医疗中心|艾森豪威尔医疗中心]]去世，终年84岁<ref name="dies">{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1696&dat=19970918&id=3csaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=10cEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6854,2265237 | title = Comedian, actor Red Skelton dies at age 84 | author = Horn, John | date = 1997-09-18 | publisher = Daily News Bowling Green, Kentucky | page = 6B | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222172705/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1696&dat=19970918&id=3csaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=10cEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6854,2265237 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，身后遗骨下葬在加利福尼亚州[[格伦代尔_(加利福尼亚州)|格伦代尔]][[森林草坪纪念公园_(格伦代尔)|森林草坪纪念公园]]的大陵园祝祷圣殿家族私有墓室，和他的儿子理查德、前妻乔治娅永远躺在了一起<ref name="Hyatt-2004" />{{rp|156}}<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1350&dat=19780430&id=qgtPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=aAIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7143,3065117 | title = Cemeteries Provide Recollections From Past | author = Seff, Marsha Kay | date = 1978-04-30 | publisher = Toledo Blade | page = 4 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-12-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222163239/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1350&dat=19780430&id=qgtPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=aAIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7143,3065117 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=tv5RAAAAIBAJ&sjid=RXYDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5171,2035166&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | title = Torrents Of Tears Well In Red's Twinkling Eyes | author = Bacon, James | date = 1958-05-14 | publisher = St. Petersburg Times | page = 15A | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150912044940/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=tv5RAAAAIBAJ&sjid=RXYDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5171,2035166&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他的身后人包括遗孀洛锡安·托兰德·斯克尔顿、女儿瓦伦蒂娜·玛丽·斯克里顿·阿隆索和外孙女萨布丽娜·莫琳·阿隆索（{{lang|en|Sabrina Maureen Alonso}}）<ref name="NYTObit" /><ref name="Divorce" />。

== 绘画和其他兴趣 ==
=== 画作 ===
[[File:Red_Skelton_with_artwork_1948.jpg|thumb]]
斯克尔顿从1943年开始绘图，但之后多年都没有公开。据他所说，自己是在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]一家大型[[百货公司|百货公司]]看到陈列的多种画作后受到启发开始试着作画。斯克尔顿当时问起一幅看起来就是“一堆斑点”的画作价格，店员的回答是“一万人里也没有一个能买得起。”他又告诉店员说，自己是那一万人中不会买这幅画、但会买艺术品原料的一个。他的夫人乔治娅曾进修美术，她说服丈夫于1964年在拉斯维加斯金沙酒店表演期间开办第一场公开作品展<ref name="Gehring-2008" />{{rp|280-282}}<ref name="Art">{{cite news | publisher = Park City Daily News | page = 14 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | title = Red Skelton's Paintings Exhibited At Las Vegas | author = Gavin, Mike | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=owwdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AZcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7263,4009494&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | date = 1964-06-21 | archive-date = 2015-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908163346/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=owwdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AZcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7263,4009494&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。斯克尔顿将绘画视为自己喜剧作品中的资产，因为这有助于他更好把自己哑剧表演中的所需要的道具想像出来<ref name="classic" />。

斯克尔顿出售的画作中不但有原作，也有通过自己专门的邮购业务出售的复制品和印刷品<ref name="welcome" />。直接向美术馆出售画作的同时，他也会出售作品的特许经营权<ref name="millionaire" />。他曾估算自己一年单凭销售[[平版印刷|平版画]]就赚了250万美元<ref name="NYTObit" />{{#tag:ref|虽然知晓自己作品的价值，但斯克尔顿并未站在严格的货币立场上来看待这些作品。他经常会对眼前的事物做即兴素描——餐厅的亚麻餐巾就是常见的主题——然后拿给遇到的崇拜者看<ref name="millionaire" />。|name=napkin|group="注"}}。斯克尔顿辞世后不久，他的艺术品经销商表示，斯克尔顿通过画作所赚的钱很可能比电视领域更高<ref name="People2">{{cite web |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325041637/http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0%2C%2C20123383%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-03-25 |url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20123383,00.html |title=Good Night and God Bless |author=Castro, Peter |work=People |accessdate=2014-08-07 }}</ref>。斯克尔顿生前共绘制了上千幅小丑的油画。当他人问起他为什么要在画作中专注于小丑时，他起初这样回答：“我不知道为什么总是小丑。”接下来他又想了一会，然后再说：“我，并不是这样——我知道为什么。我只是不喜欢去考虑这件事……”<ref name="LAobit" />{{#tag:ref|斯克尔顿也画过很多鸭子，到1973年时已经完成了超过3000幅。他会把自己不喜欢的画扔进垃圾堆，结果回收他家垃圾的人把这些丢弃的作品挽救回来并卖了出去<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1368&dat=19730630&id=hndQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WxEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7375,3595986 | title = No Wisequacks! Skelton Paints Ducks | author = Wilson, Earl | date = 1973-06-30 | work = The Milwaukee Sentinel | page = 23 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2016-05-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160508204039/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1368&dat=19730630&id=hndQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=WxEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7375,3595986 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。|name=ducks|group="注"}}斯克尔顿的单幅原作在他去世时的价格达到8万美元以上<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1310&dat=19970918&id=WABRAAAAIBAJ&sjid=h-sDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5857,4387092 | title = Red Skelton, Beloved Clown, Dies At 84 | date = 1997-09-18 | publisher = Eugene Register-Guard | page = 4A | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2016-04-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160429141721/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1310&dat=19970918&id=WABRAAAAIBAJ&sjid=h-sDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5857,4387092 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 其他兴趣 ===
斯克尔顿是位多产的短篇故事作家和[[作曲家|作曲家]]。他晚上只睡4到5小时，早上5点起床，然后开始写故事、作曲、绘画。他每星期都至少会写一篇短篇故事，一生中创作的歌曲和[[交响乐|交响乐曲]]达8000多首<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1-dUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=gTwNAAAAIBAJ&pg=1044,6106790&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | title = Red Skelton complex but happy | date = 1967-04-27 | publisher = The Leader-Post | page = 6 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908163302/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1-dUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=gTwNAAAAIBAJ&pg=1044,6106790&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他为[[干杯_(烟草)|干杯烟草]]写过广告，还把自己的许多作品卖给了专为商店和其它企业提供[[背景音乐|背景音乐]]的[[米尤扎克|米尤扎克]]（{{lang|en|Muzak}}）公司<ref name="People" />。斯克尔顿还对摄影感兴趣，参加好莱坞的许多聚会时，他会先拍照片，然后把胶卷送给只能在外面等待的报社记者<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HSIrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pZwFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3958,5064036&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | title = Red Skelton Debunks Impression All Clowns Just Like a Pagliacci | date = 1962-11-11 | publisher = Reading Eagle | page = 57 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150912050838/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HSIrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pZwFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3958,5064036&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他身上总是带有微型相机，而且保有自己所有画作的照片记录<ref name="classic" />。斯克尔顿还是狂热的园艺爱好者，他在加利福尼亚州棕榈泉的家里栽培[[盆景|盆景]]，还创建了自己的[[日本|日本]]和[[意大利|意大利]]风格花园<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MGEqAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AU8EAAAAIBAJ&pg=3971,1064159&dq=red+skelton+bridge&hl=en | title = Stars In Exodus From Hollywood | author = Hopper, Hedda | date = 1964-03-19 | publisher = The Pittsburgh Press | page = 2B | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908174345/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MGEqAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AU8EAAAAIBAJ&pg=3971,1064159&dq=red+skelton+bridge&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ZMpNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=MooDAAAAIBAJ&pg=7320,5180769&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | title = Red Skelton Insulates Self Against Misfortune | author = Thomas, Bob | date = 1965-03-09 | publisher = The Free Lance-Star | page = 2 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910052329/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ZMpNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=MooDAAAAIBAJ&pg=7320,5180769&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 联谊会和荣誉 ==
斯克尔顿是[[共济会|共济会]]成员，属印第安纳州温森斯一号会所。他还是[[苏格兰仪式|苏格兰共济会]]和[[约克仪式|约克共济会]]的成员<ref name="masonry">{{cite web |url=http://www.araratshrine.com/history/famous/redskelton/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407081345/http://www.araratshrine.com/history/famous/redskelton/ |title=Red Skelton |publisher=Ararat Shrine Temple |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archivedate=2014-04-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。他曾因在艺术与科学领域的杰出贡献获共济会分会会员普通大议会金质奖章。1969年9月24日，他获得了苏格兰仪式第33级荣誉，而且是1995年格尔加斯勋章得主<ref name="masonry" /><ref>{{cite web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325065312/http://itctel.com/~docsue/red.html | title = Red Skelton wins top Scottish Rite honor | publisher = The Northern Light | year = 1995 | accessdate = 2014-03-25 | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | url = http://itctel.com/~docsue/red.html }}</ref>。斯克尔顿儿时曾在温森斯的街头卖报，一位男子用一张5美元的钞票买了一份报纸，还告诉他不用找钱了。年幼的斯克尔顿问起对方为什么要给自己这么多钱，对方告诉他，自己是共济会成员，从小就被教导着要给予。这一经历让斯克尔顿对共济会产生了兴趣，决心长大后也要成为其中一员<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.muratshrine.org/bios/skelton.php | title = An Afternoon With Red Skelton | author = Sawyer, Tommy E. | date = 1998 Fall | publisher = The Texas Mason | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archivedate = 2014-03-25 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325060351/http://www.muratshrine.org/bios/skelton.php }}</ref>。他还是洛杉矶[[圣地兄弟会|圣地兄弟会]]的成员<ref name="masonry" />。

斯克尔顿是[[杜鲁门州立大学|杜鲁门州立大学]][[斐陶斐声誉学会|斐陶斐声誉学会]]的荣誉会员<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2011-02-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110220185929/http://web.ics.purdue.edu/~phisig/famous.php | deadurl = yes | url = http://web.ics.purdue.edu/~phisig/famous.php | title = Famous Phi Sigs | publisher = Phi Sigma Kappa at Purdue University | accessdate = 2014-08-07 }}</ref>。1961年，他获得了[[爱默生学院|爱默生学院]]约瑟夫·{{lang|en|E}}·康纳奖通信领域卓越贡献奖和荣誉学位，并成为学院{{lang|el|ΦΑΤ}}兄弟会荣誉成员<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DDY_AAAAIBAJ&sjid=UFEMAAAAIBAJ&pg=2084,4084041&dq=richard+skelton&hl=en | title = College Honors Comic With Honorary Degree | date = 1961-11-06 | publisher = The Windsor Star | page = 20 | archive-date = 2015-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908152550/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=DDY_AAAAIBAJ&sjid=UFEMAAAAIBAJ&pg=2084,4084041&dq=richard+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。斯克尔顿从温森斯高中获得了荣誉高中文凭<ref>{{cite web | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=w-9GAAAAIBAJ&sjid=oHoMAAAAIBAJ&pg=6688,611536&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | title = Triple Honors for Red Skelton | date = 1961-11-08 | publisher = Warsaw Times | page = 5 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908191841/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=w-9GAAAAIBAJ&sjid=oHoMAAAAIBAJ&pg=6688,611536&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。他还是[[卡帕・阿尔法・珀西联谊会|卡帕・阿尔法・珀西联谊会]]全美荣誉乐队的荣誉成员，全美有上万个高中或高校乐队采用他创作的多首进行曲<ref name="talents" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kkpsi.org/prominentmembers.asp |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140326171857/http://www.kkpsi.org/prominentmembers.asp |title=Prominent Members of Kappa Kappa Psi Fraternity |publisher=Kappa Kappa Psi fraternity |accessdate=2014-08-07 |archivedate=2014-03-26 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。1986年，斯克尔顿又获得了[[鲍尔州立大学|鲍尔州立大学]]的荣誉学位<ref>{{cite news | page = 15 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ePIhAAAAIBAJ&sjid=e9UEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5100,5822982&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | title = Red is honored | date = 1986-09-19 | publisher = The Nevada Daily Mail | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150912054611/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ePIhAAAAIBAJ&sjid=e9UEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5100,5822982&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

横跨[[沃巴什河|沃巴什河]]的[[雷德·斯克尔顿纪念大桥|雷德·斯克尔顿纪念大桥]]将[[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]]和[[印第安纳州|印第安纳州]]连接起来，是[[50号美国国道|50号美国国道]]的组成部分，桥的位置接近斯克尔顿的故乡温森斯，他于1963年出席了命名仪式<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QcsVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=6BAEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5178,2958107&dq=red+skelton+bridge&hl=en | title = Earl Wilson | author = Wilson, Earl | date = 1963-09-12 | publisher = The Milwaukee Journal | page = 11 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150912060241/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QcsVAAAAIBAJ&sjid=6BAEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5178,2958107&dq=red+skelton+bridge&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 奖项和表彰 ==
[[File:Hollywood_Star_Red_Skelton.jpg|thumb]]
1952年，斯克尔顿获得了[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]最佳喜剧节目和最佳喜剧演员奖<ref name="pain">{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=uVIcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7VEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6789,2698521&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | title = Skelton Honored at Emmys, Recalls Pain of Cancellation | date = 1986-09-22 | publisher = The Dispatch | page = 18 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910053015/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=uVIcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7VEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6789,2698521&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="database">{{cite web |archivedate=2014-03-25 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325044631/http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominations/award-search?search_api_views_fulltext=red%20skelton&submit=Search&search_api_views_fulltext_1=&search_api_views_fulltext_3=&search_api_views_fulltext_2=&search_api_views_fulltext_4=&field_nominations_year=All&field_nomination_category=All |url=http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominations/award-search?search_api_views_fulltext=red+skelton&submit=Search&search_api_views_fulltext_1=&search_api_views_fulltext_3=&search_api_views_fulltext_2=&search_api_views_fulltext_4=&field_nominations_year=All&field_nomination_category=All |title=Emmy Awards Database-Red Skelton |publisher=Academy of Television Arts & Sciences |accessdate=2014-08-07 }}</ref>。他还于1957年因《[[90分钟剧场|90分钟剧场]]》中诠释《大滑道》（{{lang|en|''The Big Slide''}}）这一非喜剧类演出获得一项艾美奖提名（{{lang|en|''Playhouse 90''}}）<ref name="Emmy">{{cite web | url = http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominees-winners/1957/actor-general | title = Red Skelton for 'The Big Slide', ''Playhouse 90'' | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | year = 1957 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140506233627/http://www.emmys.com/awards/nominees-winners/1957/actor-general | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archivedate = 2014-05-06 }}</ref>。1961年，斯克尔顿与自己节目的编剧一起获得了艾美奖最佳喜剧编剧奖<ref name="pain" /><ref name="database" />。1968和1969年，他两度成为[[林林兄弟和巴纳姆及贝利小丑大学|林林兄弟和巴纳姆及贝利小丑大学]]荣誉教员<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19691024&id=qExSAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9XsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2524,2689567 | title = Clown College Again Honors Red Skelton | date = 1969-10-24 | publisher = St. Petersburg Times | page = 4B | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2016-05-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160506062403/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19691024&id=qExSAAAAIBAJ&sjid=9XsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2524,2689567 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

离开电视业界后，斯克尔顿获得的第一项重要表彰是1978年[[好莱坞外国记者协会|好莱坞外国记者协会]]授予他的[[塞西尔·B·德米尔奖|塞西尔·B·德米尔奖]]，感谢他对娱乐业作出的杰出贡献。当时他走上舞台接过奖杯，台下众人起立鼓掌，他心中非常激动，手中抓得太紧，以致于奖杯都破裂了<ref name="gg">{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1842&dat=19780127&id=N_srAAAAIBAJ&sjid=98YEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3216,4704056 | title = Director Herbert Ross Sweeps Movie Categories | date = 1978-01-27 | publisher = Times Daily | page = 8 | accessdate = 2014-08-05 | archive-date = 2016-04-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425134317/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1842&dat=19780127&id=N_srAAAAIBAJ&sjid=98YEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3216,4704056 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1986年，他获得了[[美国电视艺术与科学学院|美国电视艺术与科学学院]]颁发的主席奖，全场观众起立鼓掌。掌声平息下来后他说：“我想感谢你坐下来，我以为你们打算像哥伦比亚广播公司那样抛下我不管，就这样走出去呢”<ref name="NYTObit" /><ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-RUpAAAAIBAJ&sjid=QYQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6914,3828592&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | title = Skelton will receive highest academy honor | date = 1986-07-25 | publisher = The Deseret News | page = A3 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150908165527/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-RUpAAAAIBAJ&sjid=QYQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6914,3828592&dq=red+skelton&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，这份荣誉到来之时，他的电视节目停播已有16个年头<ref name="academy" />。

1987年，斯克尔顿获得了[[美国演员工会奖|美国演员工会奖]]终身成就奖，1988年，他得以入选美国电视艺术与科学学院电视名人堂<ref name="TVhall">{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8qFSAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8X4DAAAAIBAJ&pg=1785,708688&dq=red+skelton+clown+hall+of+fame&hl=en | title = Eight inducted into TV Academy Hall of Fame | date = 1989-01-20 | publisher = Palo Verde Valley Times | page = 2 | accessdate = 2014-08-05 | archive-date = 2015-09-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910051701/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8qFSAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8X4DAAAAIBAJ&pg=1785,708688&dq=red+skelton+clown+hall+of+fame&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | publisher = Gettysburg Times | page = 7A | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2202&dat=19871203&id=S_IlAAAAIBAJ&sjid=v_wFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2565,2905034 | title = People-Red Skelton | date = 1987-12-03 | archive-date = 2016-05-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160506044220/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2202&dat=19871203&id=S_IlAAAAIBAJ&sjid=v_wFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2565,2905034 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Television Hall of Fame Archives | url = http://www.emmys.com/awards/hall-of-fame-honorees | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140626213714/http://www.emmys.com/awards/hall-of-fame-honorees | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archivedate = 2014-06-26 }}</ref>。1989年，他成为最早入选[[国际小丑名人堂|国际小丑名人堂]]的其中一人<ref name="Danilov-1997">{{cite book | page = [https://archive.org/details/halloffamemuseum00dani/page/169 169] | title = Hall of Fame Museums: A Reference Guide | url = https://archive.org/details/halloffamemuseum00dani | publisher = Greenwood Publishing Group | year = 1997 | first = Victor J. | last = Danilov | isbn = 978-0-313-30000-4}}</ref><ref name="Heim-2007">{{cite book | title = Exploring Indiana Highways: Trip Trivia | publisher = Exploring America's Highway | year = 2007 | first = Michael | last = Heim | isbn = 978-0-974-43583-1 | page = 200}}</ref>；同年他还与[[凯瑟琳·赫本|凯瑟琳·赫本]]一起获得美国喜剧奖的终身成就奖<ref name="comedyaward">{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1144&dat=19890524&id=wpMcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=f2MEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6961,4673105 | title = Hepburn, Skelton among comedy honorees | publisher = The Pittsburgh Press | date = 1989-05-24 | page = C11 | accessdate = 2014-08-05 | archive-date = 2016-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160512154729/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1144&dat=19890524&id=wpMcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=f2MEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6961,4673105 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=XG8aAAAAIBAJ&sjid=4CsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5584,584651&dq=red+skelton+clown+hall+of+fame&hl=en | title = Performance by Red Skelton to aid Circus World Museum | date = 1989-05-02 | publisher = The Milwaukee Journal | page = 5B | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150912053534/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=XG8aAAAAIBAJ&sjid=4CsEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5584,584651&dq=red+skelton+clown+hall+of+fame&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1994年，他又得以入选[[国家广播名人堂|国家广播名人堂]]<ref name="hof" />。他在[[好莱坞星光大道|好莱坞星光大道]]上分别因在广播和电视上的贡献而各有一颗星星<ref name="fame" />。

== 影响 ==
斯克尔顿希望他人视他为小丑而非滑稽演员：“一个喜剧演员出场后，马上就会和他人打成一片。而小丑采用的是悲怆。他可能很有趣，然后又会直转而下，用真正生活的感受触及人们的内心，打动他们”<ref name="circusclown" />。他还说：“我只想让人们记得我是个小丑，因为对我来说，这正是我职业上的高度。这意味着你无所不能——能唱、能跳，并且最重要的是，让人开怀大笑”<ref name="NYTObit" /><ref name="fame">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140106074804/http://projects.latimes.com/hollywood/star-walk/red-skelton/ | archivedate = 2014-01-06 | url = http://projects.latimes.com/hollywood/star-walk/red-skelton/ | title = Red Skelton-Hollywood Walk of Fame | publisher = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2014-08-07 }}</ref>。他深信，自己生命的意义，就是要给人带去欢笑<ref name="Life" />。

[[格鲁乔·马克思|格鲁乔·马克思]]在《格鲁乔与我》中认为，斯克尔顿是“演艺界最被低估的小丑”，是“[[查理·卓别林|卓别林]]最合乎逻辑的继承人”，这主要是因为他能够以最少的对话和道具表现众多角色。格鲁乔用这样的话来描绘自己亲眼见证的一场表演：“只用软边帽这一个道具，他就成功地把自己转变成一个白痴般的男孩、一位暴躁的老妇人、一个摇摇欲坠的蹒跚醉汉、一个吃得太多的女人、一个流浪汉，以及其他任何能够满足他幻想的角色。这里没有稀奇古怪的妆底、没有滑稽的服装，只有雷德。”他还补充道，斯克尔顿能够“像任何一位严肃演员那样表演戏剧性的镜头。”<ref name="Gehring-2008" />{{rp|preface, xv}}<ref name="Marx-1959">{{cite book | title = Groucho And Me | publisher = Da Capo Press | year = 1959 | isbn = 978-0-306-80666-7 | first = Groucho | last = Marx | pages = 136–137}}</ref>。1965年末，[[腹语术|腹语]]表演艺术家[[埃德加·伯根|埃德加·伯根]]（{{lang|en|Edgar Bergen}}）在回顾娱乐圈时特别给予斯克尔顿高度评价：“今天，一切都截然不同。整个喜剧界的面貌都已经有了根本性的改变——从15分钟的品质向数量转变。我们身边有许多非常风趣的人，从[[查利·蔡斯|查利·蔡斯]]（{{lang|en|Charley Chase}}）到查理·卓别林以及[[劳莱与哈台|劳莱与哈台]]。这群人中的最后一位，就是雷德·斯克尔顿”<ref>{{cite news | format = PDF | url = http://www.fultonhistory.com/Newpapers%20Disk2/Utica%20NY%20Daily%20Observer/Utica%20NY%20Observer%201965%20pdf/Utica%20NY%20Observer%201965%20a%20-%204266.PDF#xml=http://www.fultonhistory.com/dtSearch/dtisapi6.dll?cmd=getpdfhits&u=ffffffff8bdbc9e4&DocId=2183107&Index=Z%3a%5cIndex%20U%2dF%2dP&HitCount=6&hits=18+19+28+29+327+328+&SearchForm=C%3a%5cinetpub%5cwwwroot%5cFulton%5fNew%5fform%2ehtml&.pdf | title = You Can Go Back to Allen's Alley Sunday Night | date = 1965-11-12 | publisher = Utica Observer-Dispatch | page = 11 | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archive-date = 2015-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924020025/http://www.fultonhistory.com/Newpapers%20Disk2/Utica%20NY%20Daily%20Observer/Utica%20NY%20Observer%201965%20pdf/Utica%20NY%20Observer%201965%20a%20-%204266.PDF#xml=http://www.fultonhistory.com/dtSearch/dtisapi6.dll?cmd=getpdfhits&u=ffffffff8bdbc9e4&DocId=2183107&Index=Z%3a%5cIndex%20U%2dF%2dP&HitCount=6&hits=18+19+28+29+327+328+&SearchForm=C%3a%5cinetpub%5cwwwroot%5cFulton%5fNew%5fform%2ehtml&.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[哥伦比亚电影公司|哥伦比亚电影公司]]的[[哈里·考恩|哈里·考恩]]（{{lang|en|Harry Cohn}}）也称赞了斯克尔顿，称：“他是老传统的小丑。他不需要妙语，他有真诚的心”<ref name="academy" />。
[[File:Marcel_marceau_red_skelton_in_1965.JPG|thumb]]同台演出，两人也是多年的朋友。]]

斯克尔顿和[[马塞尔·马索|马塞尔·马索]]有着长时间的友谊，并且都很钦佩对方的工作。马索曾3次走上斯克尔顿在哥伦比亚广播公司的电视节目，其中包括1961年的一次担任主持人，当时斯克尔顿因手术尚在恢复中而无法前来<ref name="faces" />。他还在斯克尔顿为{{lang|en|HBO}}制作的3期《甜姐儿》特别节目中[[友情客串|客串出镜]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19820316&id=6_QNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VHsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2644,323423 | title = Red Skelton, America's consummate clown, is always in character | author = Benbow, Charles | date = 1982-03-16 | publisher = St. Petersburg Times | page = 1D | accessdate = 2014-08-08 | archive-date = 2016-05-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160502024153/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19820316&id=6_QNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=VHsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2644,323423 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。马索在斯克尔顿逝世后一次接受《[[电视指南_(杂志)|电视指南]]》采访时说：“雷德，对于我以及千千万万因你欢笑和哭泣的人来说，你都是永恒的。愿上帝永远保佑你，我伟大而珍贵的同伴。我永远都不会忘记我们共同创建的那个无声的世界”<ref name="Hyatt-2004" />{{rp|157}}。哥伦比亚广播公司在斯克尔顿与世长辞之际发布了这样的声明：“雷德的观众群没有年龄限制。他是完美的家庭艺人——迷人的小丑、举世无双的故事家、精湛的默剧大师、歌唱家和舞蹈家”<ref name="dies" />。

2006年2月，雷德·斯克尔顿表演艺术中心在温森斯大学落成，这里距斯克尔顿在温森斯的出生地仅有一个街区<ref name="Arts" /><ref name="town">{{cite news | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2006/jun/11/nation/na-skelton11 | title = Town Honors Red Skelton With Theater | date = 2006-06-11 | publisher = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2014-08-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325093154/http://articles.latimes.com/2006/jun/11/nation/na-skelton11 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-25 }}</ref>。这里有一间拥有850个座位的剧院，并配有教室、排练室和更衣室。其大厅是展览斯克尔顿画作、雕塑和海报的画廊<ref name="foundation">{{cite web |url=http://www.vinu.edu/content/red-skelton-foundation |title=Red Skelton Foundation |publisher=Red Skelton Foundation |accessdate=2014-08-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729093735/http://www.vinu.edu/content/red-skelton-foundation |archivedate=2014-07-29 }}</ref>。剧院内主要举办温森斯大学制作的戏剧和音乐节目演出，也是特别活动、集会和会议的举办地<ref name="Arts">{{cite web |url=http://www.vinu.edu/content/center |title=Red Skelton Performing Arts Center |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729091904/http://vinu.edu/content/center |publisher=Vincennes University |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archivedate=2014-07-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2013年7月18日，雷德·斯克尔顿美国喜剧博物馆在斯克尔顿诞辰100周年之际在温森斯大学附近开幕<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.redskelton.com/#!news/c1d5m | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140701224055/http://vinu.edu/red-skelton-theater#!news/c1d5m | title = Grand Opening of the Red Skelton Museum of American Comedy | date = 2013-07-18 | publisher = official Red Skelton website | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-08-07 | archivedate = 2014-07-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vinu.edu/red-skelton-theater |title=Red Skelton Performing Arts Center |publisher=Vincennes University |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archivedate=2014-06-03 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140603225615/http://www.vinu.edu/red-skelton-theater }}</ref>。这里存放有他从10岁起就开始收集的个人和职业物品，根据他的遗愿，这些物品会在自己的故乡向公众开放。斯克尔顿的遗孀洛锡安指出，亡夫曾表示自己对任何有关好莱坞的纪念都没兴趣<ref name="foundation" />{{#tag:ref|斯克尔顿曾在1984年接受采访时表示，他从10岁起就一直保留着自己的私人物品，还称自己会“让别人看到这一切”<ref>{{cite news | publisher = Daily News Bowling Green, Kentucky | page = 15C | accessdate = 2014-08-08 | date = 1984-04-12 | url = http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1696&dat=19840412&id=uP4hAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dUcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6601,3319664 | title = Zany comedy of a classic clown still brings laughter | archive-date = 2016-04-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160427043209/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1696&dat=19840412&id=uP4hAAAAIBAJ&sjid=dUcEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6601,3319664 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。|name=kept|group="注"}}。这所博物馆由雷德·斯克尔顿博物馆基金会和[[印第安纳州历史学会|印第安纳州历史学会]]共同出资<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-06-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140610230537/http://www.indianahistory.org/about/media-resources/red-skelton-museum-foundation-indiana-historical-society-form-partnership | accessdate = 2014-08-08 | date = 2010-09-09 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.indianahistory.org/about/media-resources/red-skelton-museum-foundation-indiana-historical-society-form-partnership | title = Red Skelton Museum Foundation, Indiana Historical Society Form Partnership | publisher = Indiana Historical Society }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://mywabashvalley.com/fulltext?nxd_id=156416 | title = Red Skelton Museum Gets One Million Dollar Donation | date = 2010-11-22 | publisher = My Wabash Valley | author = Shane, Katie | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120320115245/http://mywabashvalley.com/fulltext?nxd_id=156416 | accessdate = 2012-03-20 | archivedate = 2012-03-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = Hitchcock, Allie | date = 2012-07-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808014308/http://www.courierpress.com/news/local-news/no-headline-redskeltongrant | url = http://www.courierpress.com/news/2012/jul/16/no-headline---redskeltongrant/ | title = Lilly Endowment will aid Vincennes University in completing Red Skelton museum | publisher = Evansville Courier and Press | accessdate = 2014-08-08 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-08 }}</ref>。基金会的其它项目包括为温森斯的低收入家庭儿童提供新衣服等<ref name="faces" />。基金会还买下了斯克尔顿的出生地，并且继续出资对其加以修复<ref name="foundation" /><ref>{{cite web | publisher = Historic Vincennes-Knox County | url = http://www.vincennescvb.org/attractions/18/points-of-interest/291/red-skelton-birthplace | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503045715/http://www.vincennescvb.org/attractions/18/points-of-interest/291/red-skelton-birthplace | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | title = Red Skelton Birthplace | accessdate = 2014-08-08 }}</ref>。历史悠久的温森斯万神殿剧院也在继续进行修复，斯克尔顿年轻时曾在这里演出<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pantheontheatre.com/ | title = Pantheon Theatre | publisher = Pantheon Theatre | accessdate = 2014-08-08 | archivedate = 2014-01-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140109231125/http://pantheontheatre.com/ }}</ref>。

温森斯自2005年就开始举办一年一度的雷德·斯克尔顿节。节日期间会有号称[[美国中西部|美国中西部]]最大规模小丑游行的“千名小丑巡游”，其后是各种面向家庭的娱乐活动以及现场音乐表演<ref name="Clowns">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100413135510/http://www.redskeltonfestival.com/info.htm | archivedate = 2010-04-13 | url = http://www.redskeltonfestival.com/info.htm | title = Red Skelton Tribute Festival | accessdate = 2010-04-13 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2014-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140503080347/http://www.release-news.com/index.php/arts-a-entertainment/5099-red-skelton-tribute-artist-brian-hoffman-attending-fifth-annual-red-skelton-festival-vincennes-ind.html | url = http://www.release-news.com/index.php/arts-a-entertainment/5099-red-skelton-tribute-artist-brian-hoffman-attending-fifth-annual-red-skelton-festival-vincennes-ind.html | title = Red Skelton Tribute Artist Brian Hoffman Attending Fifth Annual Red Skelton Festival, Vincennes Ind | year = 2010 | publisher = release-news.com | accessdate = 2014-08-08 }}</ref>。

